    public class BeamValuesRel
extends Values
implements BeamRelNode
    BeamRelNode to replace a Values node.

    BeamValuesRel will be used in the following SQLs:

    • insert into t (name, desc) values ('hello', 'world')
    • select 1, '1', LOCALTIME
